{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A sickness spreads through the roots of the Nine Worlds, withering the ancient blue roses. As Yggdrasil's branches decay, shadows of old gods stir once more.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play as a lone wanderer in the lands of your ancestors. Haunted by dark forces at every step, you must rediscover ancient runic powers and cleanse these cursed realms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore this grim Norse world and uncover the secrets that lie beneath. Use precise combat and tactical prowess to overcome dangerous creatures and towering bosses. Gather <i>runic powers</i> and <i>ancient magics</i> to aid you on your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088300/extras/Combat_GIF_2.gif?t=1732272884\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Explore an Interconnected World</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Journey from the misty paths of the Whispering Woods to the depths of ancient temples. Each corner holds new dangers and secrets waiting to be discovered.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088300/extras/Mockup_CaveT03.gif?t=1732272884\" /><strong>Master Tactical Combat</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every enemy has unique attack patterns and weaknesses. Master timing and positioning to overcome your foes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088300/extras/Nattvaka_Intro_GIF.gif?t=1732272884\" /><strong>Discover Ancient Powers</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock new abilities throughout your journey. Use these powers to reach new areas, defeat powerful enemies, and uncover hidden paths.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088300/extras/Dash_Ability_GIF.gif?t=1732272884\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088300/extras/divider-02_620.png?t=1732272884\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Challenging, tactical combat system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Interconnected world with meaningful exploration</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Multiple abilities and power-ups to discover</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hand-crafted pixel art environments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Norse mythology-inspired setting</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Atmospheric soundtrack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hidden secrets and optional challenges</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unique bosses to overcome</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088300/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732272884","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088300/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1732272884","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088300/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1732272884","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088300/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1732272884","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Captions available","id":13}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":3325100,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A sickness spreads through the roots of the Nine Worlds, withering the ancient blue roses. As Yggdrasil's branches decay, shadows of old gods stir once more.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play as a lone wanderer in the lands of you